{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01BgWHnayMvhbicAEgtezWiG","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Report: CloseCall On-Chain State Definitions\n\nBased on the three sources, here are the complete account structures the decoder needs to handle:\n\n### CloseCallConfig Account\n\n**PDA Seeds**: `[\"closecall_config\"]`\n\n**Discriminator**: `[223, 10, 131, 227, 39, 34, 132, 36]`\n\n**Fields**:\n- `authority: Pubkey` — Admin authority (can update config, force close)\n- `treasury: Pubkey` — Fee destination wallet\n- `pyth_feed_id: [u8; 32]` — Pyth price feed ID for BTC/USD\n- `betting_window_secs: u32` — Betting window duration in seconds (default 30)\n- `max_entries_per_side: u8` — Maximum entries per side (default 32)\n- `paused: bool` — Whether the game is paused\n- `bump: u8` — Bump seed for PDA derivation\n\n### CloseCallRound Account\n\n**PDA Seeds**: `[\"cc_round\", &round_id]`\n\n**Discriminator**: `[205, 51, 62, 226, 33, 11, 235, 40]`\n\n**Fields**:\n- `round_id: [u8; 8]` — Backend-generated random round ID (used in PDA seeds)\n- `server: Pubkey` — Server wallet that paid rent and will settle\n- `phase: CloseCallPhase` — Current phase (enum below)\n- `green_entries: Vec<BetEntry>` — Green (bull) entries (max 32)\n- `red_entries: Vec<BetEntry>` — Red (bear) entries (max 32)\n- `green_pool: u64` — Total lamports in green pool\n- `red_pool: u64` — Total lamports in red pool\n- `open_price: i64` — Pyth open price at round creation (scaled integer)\n- `open_price_expo: i32` — Pyth price exponent at round creation\n- `close_price: i64` — Pyth close price at settlement (0 until settled)\n- `created_at: i64` — Unix timestamp when round was created\n- `betting_ends_at: i64` — Unix timestamp when betting window closes\n- `resolve_deadline: i64` — Unix timestamp after which timeout_refund is available\n- `outcome: Outcome` — Settlement outcome (enum below)\n- `total_fee: u64` — Fee collected (0 for refund rounds)\n- `bump: u8` — Bump seed for PDA derivation\n\n### BetEntry Struct (embedded in round)\n\n**Fields**:\n- `player: Pubkey`\n- `amount_lamports: u64`\n\n### Enum Variants\n\n**CloseCallPhase**:\n- `Open` — Round is open for bets (first 30s of candle)\n- `Settled` — Outcome determined, payouts distributed\n- `Refunded` — All bets refunded (invalid round, timeout, or force close)\n\n**Outcome**:\n- `Pending` — Settlement not yet determined\n- `Green` — Green side won\n- `Red` — Red side won\n- `Refund` — Refund outcome\n\n### RoundSettled Event\n\n**Discriminator**: `[249, 225, 66, 54, 157, 200, 234, 222]`\n\n**Fields**:\n- `round_id: [u8; 8]`\n- `outcome: Outcome`\n- `open_price: i64`\n- `close_price: i64`\n- `green_pool: u64`\n- `red_pool: u64`\n- `total_fee: u64`\n- `num_winners: u8`\n\nAll state is Anchor-serialized and uses the field naming from the generated TypeScript types (camelCase in the .ts IDL, snake_case in the JSON IDL)."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a7c729b55a6eec0ad (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 52431\ntool_uses: 3\nduration_ms: 13473</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c7e08aab-e81c-466a-b6c2-35d333150199","uuid":"3a3c2c28-c97e-4528-bbac-837e93f0139b","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read the closecall on-chain state definitions to understand what fields the decoder needs to handle. Read:\n1. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/state.rs`\n2. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/closecall.ts` (the generated types)\n3. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/closecall.json` (the IDL)\n\nReport the account structures, enum variants, and field types for CloseCallConfig and CloseCallRound.","agentId":"a7c729b55a6eec0ad","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Report: CloseCall On-Chain State Definitions\n\nBased on the three sources, here are the complete account structures the decoder needs to handle:\n\n### CloseCallConfig Account\n\n**PDA Seeds**: `[\"closecall_config\"]`\n\n**Discriminator**: `[223, 10, 131, 227, 39, 34, 132, 36]`\n\n**Fields**:\n- `authority: Pubkey` — Admin authority (can update config, force close)\n- `treasury: Pubkey` — Fee destination wallet\n- `pyth_feed_id: [u8; 32]` — Pyth price feed ID for BTC/USD\n- `betting_window_secs: u32` — Betting window duration in seconds (default 30)\n- `max_entries_per_side: u8` — Maximum entries per side (default 32)\n- `paused: bool` — Whether the game is paused\n- `bump: u8` — Bump seed for PDA derivation\n\n### CloseCallRound Account\n\n**PDA Seeds**: `[\"cc_round\", &round_id]`\n\n**Discriminator**: `[205, 51, 62, 226, 33, 11, 235, 40]`\n\n**Fields**:\n- `round_id: [u8; 8]` — Backend-generated random round ID (used in PDA seeds)\n- `server: Pubkey` — Server wallet that paid rent and will settle\n- `phase: CloseCallPhase` — Current phase (enum below)\n- `green_entries: Vec<BetEntry>` — Green (bull) entries (max 32)\n- `red_entries: Vec<BetEntry>` — Red (bear) entries (max 32)\n- `green_pool: u64` — Total lamports in green pool\n- `red_pool: u64` — Total lamports in red pool\n- `open_price: i64` — Pyth open price at round creation (scaled integer)\n- `open_price_expo: i32` — Pyth price exponent at round creation\n- `close_price: i64` — Pyth close price at settlement (0 until settled)\n- `created_at: i64` — Unix timestamp when round was created\n- `betting_ends_at: i64` — Unix timestamp when betting window closes\n- `resolve_deadline: i64` — Unix timestamp after which timeout_refund is available\n- `outcome: Outcome` — Settlement outcome (enum below)\n- `total_fee: u64` — Fee collected (0 for refund rounds)\n- `bump: u8` — Bump seed for PDA derivation\n\n### BetEntry Struct (embedded in round)\n\n**Fields**:\n- `player: Pubkey`\n- `amount_lamports: u64`\n\n### Enum Variants\n\n**CloseCallPhase**:\n- `Open` — Round is open for bets (first 30s of candle)\n- `Settled` — Outcome determined, payouts distributed\n- `Refunded` — All bets refunded (invalid round, timeout, or force close)\n\n**Outcome**:\n- `Pending` — Settlement not yet determined\n- `Green` — Green side won\n- `Red` — Red side won\n- `Refund` — Refund outcome\n\n### RoundSettled Event\n\n**Discriminator**: `[249, 225, 66, 54, 157, 200, 234, 222]`\n\n**Fields**:\n- `round_id: [u8; 8]`\n- `outcome: Outcome`\n- `open_price: i64`\n- `close_price: i64`\n- `green_pool: u64`\n- `red_pool: u64`\n- `total_fee: u64`\n- `num_winners: u8`\n\nAll state is Anchor-serialized and uses the field naming from the generated TypeScript types (camelCase in the .ts IDL, snake_case in the JSON IDL)."}],"totalDurationMs":13473,"totalTokens":52431,"totalToolUseCount":3,"usage":{"input_tokens":7,"cache_creation_input_tokens":22145,"cache_read_input_tokens":29327,"output_tokens":952,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":22145},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
